{"tid":1556631,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[ UPDATE ] 建立民間議會進度01","createTime":"2019-09-09T22:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:11:43.000Z","uid":224249,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"904c5a77e118a224577733c48d0f4df4a2a450bd","tid":1556631,"uid":224249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T22:06:17.000Z","msg":"上一次post<br />\n[ 召喚IT人 ] 成立人民議會既可行方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dNBffS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dNBffS</a><br />\n<br />\n經過第一次post，好高興有唔少人都有興趣，一齊組左一隊team。經過一輪討論同埋開會之後，有以下進展。<br />\n<br />\n進展：<br />\n更新左議會流程（目前仲有問題）<br />\n揾到一部分人加入develop team, 目前back-end team有四人（但人手仲係嚴重唔夠）<br />\n認證方式有更多既建議<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n建立民意直接影響立法的渠道<br />\n削弱現有政府既認受性, 權威<br />\n抗衡現有政府<br />\n更方便收集民意<br />\n<br />\n目前計劃：<br />\n建構一個完善既民間議會制度<br />\n目前決定一開始整responsive web, 之後視乎情況再整App.<br />\n有計劃眾籌，用途為支付web hosting fee, cloudflare plan<br />\n<br />\n建立議會既建議：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ttK3ALnYkOKI9e8cCoMlVLiCwLQy9Xzqv61NeZbBh_g/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1ttK3ALnYkOKI9e8cCoMlVLiCwLQy9Xzqv61NeZbBh_g%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=a133fd13\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ttK3ALnYkOKI9e8cCoMlVLiCwLQy9Xzqv61NeZbBh_g/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n因為時間同埋成本既關係，我地打算起一個初始版本，再視乎大家反映<br />\nMVP (Minimum Viable Product) （初始版本）<br />\n提議 -&gt; 和議 -&gt; 公投 -&gt; 通過<br />\n每一個議案就有一個telegram group,可以讓大家討論<br />\n電郵認證只可以和議議案<br />\nSMS認證後，則可以參與公投議案<br />\n<br />\n招募人手 (目前嚴重缺人)<br />\nBack-end team (Node.js)<br />\nFront-end team<br />\nUI/UX designer<br />\n其他想幫手既巴絲打<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以tg我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/nameless200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnameless200&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=a1985255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nameless200</a><br />\n<br />\n民間議會公海Group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkparliament\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkparliament&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=389695c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkparliament</a><br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n其實我都好想見到民間議會出世。可能好多人都覺得，民間議會無乜用，根本影響唔到個政府，最多都係無約束力既動議，單純只係一班人圍爐自high。但試諗下，如果有一百萬人支持呢個動議，咁個影響力一定好大，第二日都可以上報紙；如果有一百萬人唔滿意政府表現，決定罷交稅，咁對政府既影響都好大。<br />\n主權在民，或者一個人既力量影響唔到乜，但如果能夠集合大家既力量，賦予議會權力，咁就可以制衡成個政府。將來政府做決策，或者立法會審議議案，都要顧慮到議會既立場。<br />\n我好希望，能夠係咁絕望既時刻，能夠做返d野，令到大家對將來仲抱有希望。我唔知道將來會點樣，之後議會能唔能夠成功建立，係咪可以發揮到原本既功能，甚至可能會中途夭折（唔係壽終正寢）. But we won&rsquo;t know if we don&rsquo;t give a try.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，加油！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c5cbd39978a5fbeea9486cac304eb76785e36801","tid":1556631,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T22:09:15.000Z","msg":"有冇諗到點提防三毛打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993790ac0eac547e226f9f44019ac3461c2f4609","tid":1556631,"uid":296735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T22:23:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"55d17b26febfc373a327b8ea7984833bad8024f4","tid":1556631,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T22:52:22.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"fe3fa9766069e5ad6d049e12a79593e36c6da24d","tid":1556631,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T22:55:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cdb4ed005c3998f020ee8a6bb05182af565737","tid":1556631,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:00:16.000Z","msg":"[討論]HK Independence/ Return to UK,which choice will u opt<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b0b26a0db5934c11a5311239500b4d1658ac63a4","tid":1556631,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6b05482cf8467e24ccd000a2bcd5233ccb689b","tid":1556631,"uid":224249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5cbd39978a5fbeea9486cac304eb76785e36801","tid":1556631,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T22:09:15.000Z","msg":"有冇諗到點提防三毛打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:05:26.000Z","msg":"其實都有idea<br />\n但要係私隱同埋身份認證之間做個平衡，並唔容易"},{"pid":"14cff40424c139079f63b4497bcdf0983c6c5327","tid":1556631,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:06:11.000Z","msg":"個人認為只能用智庫型式存在"},{"pid":"9c2cf0d53366a9ad30fc4900323b611fac743732","tid":1556631,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a69bac34dccdd441093377e28d55704698027e","tid":1556631,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:27:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8587f58011fdb84593435834debee1f310a1c01e","tid":1556631,"uid":224249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:44:56.000Z","msg":"附上元氣彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtAw64B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtAw64B.jpg&h=59c4ea27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65b2d82c222e60fb1a73ba19f3c20ee845c70a70","tid":1556631,"uid":224249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim